<idea-plugin>
    <id>cn.cpoet.jpatcher</id>
    <name>JPatcher</name>
    <vendor email="llzero54@foxmail.com" url="https://www.cpoet.cn">CPoet</vendor>
    <description><![CDATA[
        <p><b>JPatcher</b> is an IntelliJ IDEA plugin designed to quickly generate <b>incremental patch packages</b>.</p>
        <p>The functionality of this plugin is extracted from<a href="https://github.com/c-poet/cpoet-idea-tool">CPoet Tool</a></p>
        <p>Suggest pairing <a href="https://github.com/c-poet/patch-assistant-to-java">PatchAssistant4J(补丁助手)</a> Use.</p>
        <div>
            <p><b>Main Features:</b></p>
            <ul>
                <li>🗂️ Support selecting files that require patch generation from lists such as editing windows, project trees, VCS (GIT/SVN) changes, etc</li>
                <li>⚡ Select files to quickly generate incremental patch packages in ZIP format</li>
                <li>📝 Automatically generate path instruction files and custom patch instruction file templates</li>
                <li>♻️ Support MapStruct generated Mapper files</li>
                <li>📦 Generate patch panel to support selecting dependent JAR packages</li>
                <li>🏷️ Generate change identifiers (add, mod, del) based on VCS (version management)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p><b>JPatcher</b>是一款专为IntelliJ IDEA开发的<b>增量补丁包</b>快速生成插件</p>
        <p>本插件功能提取自<a href="https://github.com/c-poet/cpoet-idea-tool">CPoet Tool</a></p>
        <p>建议搭配<a href="https://github.com/c-poet/patch-assistant-to-java">补丁助手(PatchAssistant4J)</a>使用。</p>
        <div>
            <p><b>主要功能：</b></p>
            <ul>
                <li>🗂️支持从编辑窗口、项目树、VCS(GIT/SVN)变更等列表中选择需要生成补丁的文件</li>
                <li>⚡选择文件快速生成 ZIP 格式的增量补丁包</li>
                <li>📝自动生成路径说明文件和自定义补丁说明文件模板</li>
                <li>♻️支持MapStruct生成的Mapper文件</li>
                <li>📦生成补丁面板支持选择依赖的JAR包</li>
                <li>🏷️根据VCS(版本管理)生成变化标识（新增、修改、删除）</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/c-poet/jpatcher">源代码</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.cpoet.cn">建议与反馈</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/c-poet/cpoet-idea-tool">CPoet Tool</a><p>
    ]]>
    </description>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.vcs</depends>
    <depends config-file="plugin_java.xml">com.intellij.modules.java</depends>
    <depends optional="true" config-file="plugin_mcp.xml">com.intellij.mcpServer</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <applicationConfigurable parentId="tools" instance="cn.cpoet.jpatcher.setting.Configurable" id="cn.cpoet.jpatcher.setting.Configurable" displayName="JPatcher"/>
        <notificationGroup id="JPATCHER_NOTIFICATION_BALLOON" displayType="BALLOON"/>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <group id="JPatcher_EditorPopupMenu" text="JPatcher" popup="true">
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorPopupMenu" relative-to-action="EditorToggleColumnMode" anchor="after"/>
        </group>

        <group id="JPatcher_ProjectViewPopupMenu" text="JPatcher" popup="true">
            <add-to-group group-id="ProjectViewPopupMenu" relative-to-action="AnalyzeMenu" anchor="after"/>
        </group>

        <group id="JPatcher_Vcs.RepositoryChangesBrowserMenu" text="JPatcher" popup="true">
            <add-to-group group-id="Vcs.RepositoryChangesBrowserMenu" relative-to-action="Vcs.EditSource" anchor="after" />
        </group>

        <group id="JPatcher_ChangesViewPopupMenu" text="JPatcher" popup="true">
            <add-to-group group-id="ChangesViewPopupMenu" relative-to-action="EditSource" anchor="after" />
        </group>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>